Hi Stephanie,

You can modify the maintainer name/email in the DESCRIPTION file
yourself by checking out of svn, make the change and then commit.

## release
svn co
https://hedgehog.fhcrc.org/bioconductor/branches/RELEASE_3_4/madman/Rpacks/packageName

## devel
svn co
https://hedgehog.fhcrc.org/biocondcutor/trunk/madman/Rpacks/packageName

Martin or Herve will have to give the new maintainer access to the
package repo. Do they already have an svn user name and password? What
package repo should they be added to?

Valerie







